
Podcast via https://soundcloud.com/upstreampodcast/sneak-peak-stuart-field

=Description=

"Stuart is in the process of bringing to the U.K. the popular sick-pay program for self-employed people that currently exists in the Netherlands, called Broodfunds. We spoke with him in London for our Solidarity Economy episode. Here we are featured a short excerpt from our conversation, where we go into the role of the solidarity economy in general as a force to mitigate harm and to bring about a new system."

